Package: ADImpute
Type: Package
Title: Adaptive Dropout Imputer (ADImpute)
Version: 2.1.0
Author: Ana Carolina Leote
Maintainer: Ana Carolina Leote <ana.carolina.leote@uni-koeln.de>
Description: ADImpute predicts unmeasured gene expression values from single cell
             RNA-sequencing data (dropout imputation). This R-package combines multiple
             dropout imputation methods, including a novel gene regulatory network-based method.
